'''Integrated Environmental Solutions''' (IES) Ltd. is a company that develops [[software]] simulation tools which assist [[architects]], engineers, facilities managers and all those involved in the development and management of building design, in creating healthier built environments.<ref name="Buildaroo"> [http://buildaroo.com/news/article/ies-creates-unique-climate-energy-index-system-for-sustainable-design/ "IES Creates Unique Climate Energy Index System for Sustainable Design", ''Buildaroo'', November 09 2009].</ref>

The company was established in June 1994 and is headquartered in Glasgow, Scotland, with offices in Dublin, [[Ireland]], Boston and San Francisco, [[USA]] and Melbourne, [[Australia]]. 

Offering a global portfolio of building performance consultation services and measurement products, IES’ International Consulting arm works with building design teams to provide simulation analysis and develop design solutions.<ref name="AECCafe"> [http://www10.aeccafe.com/nbc/articles/view_weekly.php?articleid=649800 "Energy and Building Performance Tools ", ''AECCafe'', February 09 2009].</ref>

